[link: /commands/categories/system.md] ’Ł@b3f5fb64d11b60db244ffb2f58505f682784a7fb47c5fce10dc1879f8f162783ŁaTitle: title: registry query
Path: Signature
Content:
``> registry query {flags} (key) (value)``
’Ł@5a20ea418f022857bdf6b00268a0dee1f908f158cb321c27bae86f7c1e1a4dd2Ś`Title: title: registry query
Path: Flags
Content:
``--hkcr``
: query the hkey_classes_root hive
``--hkcu``
: query the hkey_current_user hive
``--hklm``
: query the hkey_local_machine hive
``--hku``
: query the hkey_users hive
``--hkpd``
: query the hkey_performance_data hive
``--hkpt``
: query the hkey_performance_text hive
``--hkpnls``
: query the hkey_performance_nls_text hive
``--hkcc``
: query the hkey_current_config hive
``--hkdd``
: query the hkey_dyn_data hive
``--hkculs``
: query the hkey_current_user_local_settings hive
``--no-expand, -u``
: do not expand %ENV% placeholders in REG_EXPAND_SZ
’Ł@97658f99b3c97bee9e26dca917738bb2a9f1c5d9a6dd21db0406b5079e77356bŁ‘Title: title: registry query
Path: Parameters
Content:
``key``
: Registry key to query.
``value``
: Optionally supply a registry value to query.
’Ł@6b493a803910bbbc0ccf6ec6fe2078669d77fe78286d7dc31ac299328f297affŁYTitle: title: registry query
Path: Input/output types:
Content:
input
output
nothing
any
’Ł@73612664e4b422126861e5668b5c227ad2a17112d47b34375f7cadaa3e7e6eadŚ3Title: title: registry query
Path: Examples
Content:
Query the HKEY_CURRENT_USER hive
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> registry query --hkcu environment


```
Query the HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE hive
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> registry query --hklm 'SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Session Manager\Environment'


```
’Ł@6f0c80efa6ac6eec619a30067b770d0660859712edf9ad4bc9b3e25a39404cc5Ł_Title: title: registry query
Path: Notes
Content:
Currently supported only on Windows systems.
